Basic_description: Aluminum alloy bezel and lid structure around the display, approx. 31*19*0.5 cm.
Functional_description: Holds and protects the screen, provides stiffness and mounting points to the hinge shafts.
Movement_description: Rotates about the two hinge shafts relative to the base, allowing opening/closing of the lid with controlled friction and damping.
Grasped_description: Users typically grasp the top or sides of the frame to open or close the laptop.
